defs.name: append
defs.docs: Appends a new node to this node's children, returning a mutator of the new node.

defs.name: prepend
defs.docs: Prepends a new node to this node's children, returning a mutator of the new node.

defs.name: insert_before
defs.docs: Inserts a new sibling before this node, returning a mutator of the new node.

defs.name: insert_after
defs.docs: Inserts a new sibling after this node, returning a mutator of the new node.

defs.name: detach
defs.docs: Detaches this node from its parent.

defs.name: append_id
defs.docs: Appends a node to this node's children by ID, returning a mutator of the referenced node.

defs.name: prepend_id
defs.docs: Prepends a node to this node's children by ID, returning a mutator of the referenced node.

defs.name: insert_id_before
defs.docs: Inserts a sibling before this node by ID, returning a mutator of the referenced node.

defs.name: insert_id_after
defs.docs: Inserts a sibling after this node by ID, returning a mutator of the referenced node.

defs.name: reparent_from_id_append
defs.docs: Reparents the children of a node by ID, appending them to this node's children.

defs.name: reparent_from_id_prepend
defs.docs: Reparents the children of a node by ID, prepending them to this node's children.
